CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 30, 1966, pg. 2B reads: Wedding Guest - Lovely Wardell E. Robinson, daughter of Dr. and Mrs. Joseph B. Robinson of Albany, N.Y., was among the out-of-town guests attending the Bryan-Brown wedding at St. Richards Church recently. A senior at Albany Girls' Academy, Miss Robinson is also the godchild of the late Mrs. Daisy Lampkin. (Harris photo)"
TitMainTitle: Wardell E. Robinson wearing sleeveless dress with scarf, and gloves, posed on steps, possibly St. Richards Church, with cars and houses in background, for Bryan-Brown wedding
